ygData.subject: Re: Aqualung Sales

ygData.messageBody:
If I had the $$$ to make em I could sell aqualungs all day long! I have been
selling the scopes for 100PP each. Every dime I make goes back in to tinkering.
I unfortunately do not have a wealthy guild so am on my own here... Every person
who buys a scope does it as a donation to my tinkering fund cuz they are all
waiting for aqualungs and rebreathers. Skill 86 now... only 100 more scopes to
sell before I go in to business! =)

Focasa Ra'utha
